description: We developed a new technique named as Differential Systemic Decellularization in vivo (DISDIVO) for the molecular profiling of vascular beds throughout the body. This method can by applied to murine models. Thus, the data provided here correspond to mice vascular beds obtained in vivo by DISDIVO.
